AND CLOSE OF 5 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 9 BARS AGO

AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 2.32373 %
